{"tid":1028242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄國空軍今年將接收首架蘇-57戰機","createTime":"2019-02-19T10:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T16:10:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7aa5be119f02d57cf87f4bef9fdf899f7b6335","tid":1028242,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpwJq19t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpwJq19t.jpg&h=76f87599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄國空軍今年將接收首架量產的蘇-57戰機。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-19 17:53<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕俄國軍力再升級！俄媒報導，俄國聯合航空製造集團公司總裁斯柳薩里（Yuri Slyusar）近日受訪時透露，俄國空軍將在今年接收首架量產的蘇-57，這是俄國首架採匿蹤技術的新世代戰機。<br />\n<br />\n《俄羅斯衛星通訊社》報導，斯柳薩里昨日表示，去年8月俄國國防部主辦「軍隊-2018」國際軍事技術論壇期間，該集團與國防部簽訂2份製造蘇-57戰機和米格-35戰機的供貨合同，而首架量產型蘇-57戰機將於今年交付俄國空軍。斯柳薩里還透露，俄國國防部計劃在近期接收總共15架量產的蘇-57戰機。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，蘇-57是俄國的第五代戰機，可用於殲滅空中、地面和水下的所有目標，該戰機於2010年首次升空，具有高度的機動性，同時還可完成超音速飛行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2703447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2703447&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=a61f3c0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2703447&h=a0d29eb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2703447</a>"},{"pid":"a04aecc3067212c63407a3de5bd3b177398767b1","tid":1028242,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"整咁多軍事裝備咪又係打飛機 幾時實戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bed1bf6ce60ba384feb856ba39b187c0986441","tid":1028242,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"其實睇見前面兩個大窿都知隱形唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e493e1ebaa